instruction:
Let $a_0 = 5/2$ and $a_k = a_{k-1}^2 - 2$ for $k \geq 1$. Compute \[ \prod_{k=0}^\infty \left(1 - \frac{1}{a_k} \right) \] in closed form.

Options:
A. \frac{3}{10}
B. \frac{3}{8}
C. \frac{4}{9}
D. \frac{2}{5}
E. \frac{3}{7}
F. \frac{5}{14}
G. \frac{3}{11}
H. \frac{4}{7}
I. \frac{5}{11}
J. \frac{5}{12}
